name: CKOperationGroup.TransferSize
desc: Constants that represent possible data transfer sizes.

items.name: case kilobytes
items.desc: A transfer size that represents 1 or more kilobytes.

items.name: case megabytes
items.desc: A transfer size that represents 1 or more megabytes.

items.name: case gigabytes
items.desc: A transfer size that represents 1 or more gigabytes.

items.name: case tensOfMegabytes
items.desc: A transfer size that represents tens of megabytes.

items.name: case tensOfGigabytes
items.desc: A transfer size that represents tens of gigabytes.

items.name: case hundredsOfMegabytes
items.desc: A transfer size that represents hundreds of megabytes.

items.name: case hundredsOfGigabytes
items.desc: A transfer size that represents hundreds of gigabytes.
